      <section eId="sec_44_010">
        <num>44.010</num>
        <content>
          <p>All claims upon the State Treasury that are authorized by law shall be paid when due by the State Treasurer to the person entitled to the amount claimed. The warrant for such payment shall be issued by the Finance and Administration Cabinet upon such proof of services performed or of demand made as is required by law.</p>
